thread.title: Jason Stutes
thread.title_full: Nengun Performance について 投稿者 Jason Stutes

author: Jason Stutes
title: Jason Stutes
text:
Guys were super helpful in helping me get replacement dampers for my RMA8 setup. Impossible to get them rebuilt in the US and Silkroad is not willing to deal with shipping.
Nengun was able to contact Silkroad and get me brand new replacement dampers for the price of a rebuild....that is service.
